<!DOCTYPE html>
<!--
    references:
    - images from: DLSU CSO (Facebook Page) https://www.facebook.com/CSO.DLSU/
    - https://www.dlsu.edu.ph/students/cso/
    - https://www.w3schools.com/html/html_images.asp
    - https://www.freecodecamp.org/news/how-to-work-with-images-in-html/
    - https://codingartistweb.com/2024/12/image-gallery-with-lightbox-effect-using-html-css-and-javascript/
-->
<html>
    <head>
        <title>Council of Student Organizations (CSO) | OrgSpace</title>
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
    </head>

    <body data-org="cso@dlsu.edu.ph">
        <main>
            <nav id="menu">
                <span class="menu-title">DLSU Organizations</span>
                <input type="checkbox" id="responsive-menu"><label></label>
                <ul>
                    <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
                    <li><a class="dropdown-arrow active" href="#organizations">Organizations</a>
                        <ul class="sub-menus">
                            <li><a href="/org1">Archers for UNICEF</a></li>
                            <li><a href="/org2">Council of Student Organizations</a></li>
                            <li><a href="/org3">Information Security Organization</a></li>
                            <li><a href="/org4">La Salle Computer Society</a></li>
                            <li><a href="/org5">Management of Financial Institutions Association</a></li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                    <li><a href="/contact">Contact Us</a></li>

                    <li class="menu-profile" id="profileMenu">
                        <button class="profile-btn" id="profileBtn" aria-haspopup="true" aria-expanded="false">
                        <img src="/assets/profile-icon.png" alt="Account" class="profile-icon">
                        </button>

                        <ul class="profile-dropdown" id="profileDropdown" role="menu" aria-label="Account menu"></ul>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </nav>

            <section class="org-header">
                <div class="org-header-inner">
                    <img src="/assets/cso.png" alt="Council of Student Organizations Logo" class="org-logo">

                    <div class="org-header-text">
                        <h1>Council of Student Organizations (CSO)</h1>
                        <p class="org-tagline">
                             Always for Service.
                        </p>
                        <span class="org-category">Student Groups</span>

                        <a href="/reviews2" class="reviews-btn">See Reviews</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="org-body">
                
                <div class="org-highlights">
                    <img src="/assets/CSO1.jpg" alt="CSO Highlight 1" class="lightbox-trigger">
                    <img src="/assets/CSO2.jpg" alt="CSO Highlight 2" class="lightbox-trigger">
                    <img src="/assets/CSO3.jpg" alt="CSO Highlight 3" class="lightbox-trigger">
                </div>

                <div class="org-split">
                    <div class="org-main">
                        <div class="org-section">
                            <h2>About the Organization</h2>
                            <p>
                            The Council of Student Organizations (CSO) is the union of accredited professional (PROF), special interest (SPIN) and socio-civic organizations of De La Salle University. Since its founding in 1974, the Council has continuously delivered quality student services and has produced outstanding student leaders dedicated to serving and contributing to the Lasallian Community.
                            <br><br>
                            To support the preparation, execution, and documentation of the activities/projects/initiatives of the accredited organizations, nine Executive Teams work under the supervision of the CSO Executive Board. The CSO Executive Board also serves as the coordinating entity of the Council Body composed of the Presidents of the CSO member organizations.
                            <br><br>
                            Further CSO implements university-wide activities participated in by the different organizations. These activities include the Frosh Welcoming (FW), Annual Recruitment Week (ARW), Green Card Alliance (GCA), Award-Giving Bodies (AGB), Lasallian Excellence Awards (LEA) and the Lasallian Enrichment Alternative Program (LEAP).
                            </p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="org-section">
                            <h2>Core Values</h2>

                            <h4>Competence</h4>
                            <ul class="indented-list">
                                <li>Upholding the Lasallian brand of leadership, the Council serves as an example in innovating standards.</li>
                            </ul>

                            <h4>Service</h4>
                            <ul class="indented-list">
                                <li>Driven by the passion to serve, the Council abides by the Lasallian Core Values for the benefit of its member organizations.</li>
                            </ul>

                            <h4>Order</h4>
                            <ul class="indented-list">
                                <li>Pioneering integrity and ethics, the Council integrates these in its service and constitute discipline among its officers.</li>
                            </ul>
                            <br><br>

                            <h2>Vision-Mission</h2>
                            <p>
                                The Council of Student Organizations is committed to delivering quality services and activities as well as developing proactive and dynamic student leaders befitting the standards of a world-class research University. We create and maintain conditions where our member organizations can achieve optimum performance and realize their goals. We are driven by the ideals of the Lasallian mission, thus, we work actively to feed the needs of the students and ultimately promote the growth of their potentials.
                                <br><br>
                                The Council of Student Organizations provides relevant and quality services that support heightened student involvement and development. We continually set standards that contribute to the flourishing of our member organizations as we work together to inspire growth and create a platform for communication. We are pioneers of nation-­building and Lasallian-formation by maintaining a sense of social awareness and spiritual growth in our activities.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <aside class="org-aside">
                        <div class="org-section">
                            <h2>Current Board</h2>
                            <div class="board-cards">
                                <div class="board-card">
                                    <h4>Andreia Valderrama</h4>
                                    <span>Chairperson</span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="board-card">
                                    <h4>Denise Cudal</h4>
                                    <span>Executive Vice Chairperson for Internals</span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="board-card">
                                    <h4>Johanne Failana</h4>
                                    <span>Executive Vice Chairperson for Externals</span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="board-card">
                                    <h4>Patricia Solis</h4>
                                    <span>Executive Vice Chairperson for Documentations</span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="board-card">
                                    <h4>Joshua Ruiz</h4>
                                    <span>Executive Vice Chairperson for Finance</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </aside>
                </div>
                
                <button id="create-post-btn" class="create-post hidden">Create Post</button>

                <div class="org-section">
                    <h2>Announcements & Updates</h2>

                    <div class="org-posts">
                        <% if (posts && posts.length > 0) { %>
                            <% posts.forEach(function(post) { %>
                                <article class="org-post" id="post-<%= post._id %>">
                                    <% if (post.image) { %>
                                        <img src="<%= post.image %>" alt="<%= post.title %>" class="post-image lightbox-trigger">
                                    <% } %>
                                    
                                    <div class="post-header">
                                        <h3><%= post.title %></h3>
                                        <div class="post-actions" style="display: flex; gap: 10px; align-items: center;">
                                            <!-- Like Button -->
                                            <% if (user) { %>
                                                <% let userLiked = false; %>
                                                <% if (post.likes) { %>
                                                    <% userLiked = post.likes.some(function(like) { %>
                                                        <% return like.toString() === user.id.toString(); %>
                                                    <% }); %>
                                                <% } %>
                                                <button class="like-btn" 
                                                    data-post-id="<%= post._id %>"
                                                    data-liked-by-user="<%= userLiked %>"
                                                    style="display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 5px; background: none; border: 1px solid #046307; padding: 5px 10px; border-radius: 20px; color: #046307; cursor: pointer;">
                                                    ❤️ <span class="like-count"><%= post.likes ? post.likes.length : 0 %></span>
                                                </button>
                                            <% } %>
                                            
                                            <!-- Triple Dot Menu -->
                                            <% if (user && user.userType === 'organization' && user.email === 'cso@dlsu.edu.ph') { %>
                                                <div class="post-menu-container" style="position: relative;">
                                                    <button class="post-menu-trigger" style="background: none; border: none; font-size: 20px; cursor: pointer; padding: 0 5px;">⋮</button>
                                                    <div class="post-dropdown-menu" style="display: none; position: absolute; right: 0; background: white; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 4px; box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.2); z-index: 100;">
                                                        <button class="edit-post-btn" onclick="showEditPostModal('<%= post._id %>')" style="display: block; width: 100%; text-align: left; padding: 8px 16px; background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer; white-space: nowrap;">Edit</button>
                                                        <form action="/posts/delete/<%= post._id %>" method="POST" style="margin: 0;">
                                                            <input type="hidden" name="orgName" value="Council of Student Organizations">
                                                            <button type="submit" class="delete-post-btn" onclick="return confirm('Are you sure?')" style="display: block; width: 100%; text-align: left; padding: 8px 16px; background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer; color: #c0392b;">Delete</button>
                                                        </form>
                                                    </div>
                                                </div>
                                            <% } %>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    
                                    <span class="post-date"><%= new Date(post.createdAt).toLocaleDateString('en-US', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' }) %></span>
                                    
                                    <div class="post-content">
                                        <%- post.content.replace(/\n/g, '<br>') %>
                                    </div>
                                    
                                    <button class="comment-toggle">View comments</button>
                                    <div class="comments hidden">
                                        <% 
                                            let postComments = [];
                                            if (comments && comments.length > 0) {
                                                postComments = comments.filter(function(c) {
                                                    return c.post && c.post.toString() === post._id.toString();
                                                });
                                            }
                                        %>
                                        <% if (postComments.length > 0) { %>
                                            <% postComments.forEach(function (comment) { %>
                                                <div class="comment" data-owner="<%= comment.user ? comment.user._id : '' %>">
                                                    <div class="comment-header" style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;">
                                                        <strong style="color: #046307;">
                                                            <% if (comment.user) { %>
                                                                <% if (comment.user.userType === "admin") { %>
                                                                    Admin
                                                                <% } else if (comment.user.userType === "organization") { %>
                                                                    <%= comment.user.orgName %>
                                                                <% } else { %>
                                                                    <%= comment.user.firstName %> <%= comment.user.lastName %>
                                                                <% } %>
                                                            <% } else { %>
                                                                User
                                                            <% } %>
                                                        </strong>
                                                        
                                                        <% if (user && comment.user && (comment.user._id.toString() === user.id || user.userType === "admin")) { %>
                                                            <div class="comment-menu-container" style="position: relative;">
                                                                <button class="comment-menu-trigger" style="background: none; border: none; font-size: 16px; cursor: pointer; padding: 0 5px;">⋮</button>
                                                                <div class="comment-dropdown-menu" style="display: none; position: absolute; right: 0; background: white; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 4px; box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.2); z-index: 100;">
                                                                    <button class="edit-comment-btn" style="display: block; width: 100%; text-align: left; padding: 6px 12px; background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer; white-space: nowrap;">Edit</button>
                                                                    <form action="/delete-comment/<%= comment._id %>" method="POST" style="margin: 0;">
                                                                        <button type="submit" class="delete-comment-btn" onclick="return confirm('Delete this comment?')" style="display: block; width: 100%; text-align: left; padding: 6px 12px; background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer; color: #c0392b;">Delete</button>
                                                                    </form>
                                                                </div>
                                                            </div>
                                                        <% } %>
                                                    </div>
                                                    <p class="comment-text"><%= comment.text %></p>
                                                    
                                                    <form action="/edit-comment/<%= comment._id %>" method="POST" class="edit-comment-form hidden">
                                                        <input type="text" name="text" value="<%= comment.text %>" required>
                                                        <div class="comment-edit-actions" style="display: flex; gap: 10px; margin-top: 10px;">
                                                            <button type="submit" class="save-comment-btn" style="background: #046307; color: white; border: none; padding: 6px 12px; border-radius: 4px; cursor: pointer;">Save</button>
                                                            <button type="button" class="cancel-comment-edit-btn" style="background: #f0f0f0; color: #666; border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 6px 12px; border-radius: 4px; cursor: pointer;">Cancel</button>
                                                        </div>
                                                    </form>
                                                </div>
                                            <% }); %>
                                        <% } else { %>
                                            <p>No comments yet.</p>
                                        <% } %>
                                        
                                        <% if (user) { %>
                                            <form action="/add-comment" method="POST" class="add-comment">
                                                <textarea name="text" class="comment-input" placeholder="Write a comment..."></textarea>
                                                <input type="hidden" name="page" value="org2">
                                                <input type="hidden" name="postId" value="<%= post._id %>">
                                                <button type="submit" class="submit-comment">Post</button>
                                            </form>
                                        <% } else { %>
                                            <p class="login-warning"><a href="/login">Log in</a> to add a comment.</p>
                                        <% } %>
                                    </div>
                                </article>
                            <% }); %>
                        <% } else { %>
                            <p class="no-posts">No posts yet.</p>
                        <% } %>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
        </main>

        <!-- Edit Post Modal -->
        <div id="edit-post-modal" class="modal hidden">
            <div class="modal-content">
                <h3>Edit Post</h3>
                <form id="edit-post-form">
                    <input type="hidden" name="orgName" value="Council of Student Organizations">
                    <input type="hidden" name="postId" id="edit-post-id">
                    
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="edit-title">Title:</label>
                        <input type="text" name="title" id="edit-title" required>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="edit-content">Content:</label>
                        <textarea name="content" id="edit-content" rows="6" required></textarea>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="edit-image">Image URL:</label>
                        <input type="text" name="image" id="edit-image" placeholder="/assets/post-image.jpg">
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="modal-actions">
                        <button type="submit" class="btn-primary">Save Changes</button>
                        <button type="button" id="cancel-edit" class="btn-secondary">Cancel</button>
                    </div>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div id="create-post-modal" class="modal hidden">
            <div class="modal-content">
                <h3>Create New Post</h3>
                
                <input type="text" id="new-post-title" placeholder="Post title">
                
                <textarea id="new-post-content" placeholder="Write your announcement..."></textarea>
                
                <!-- Image selection area -->
                <div class="image-selection-area">
                    <button type="button" id="select-image-btn" class="btn-secondary">Choose Image</button>
                    <span id="selected-image-name">No image selected</span>
                    <input type="hidden" id="new-post-image" value="">
                </div>
                
                <!-- Image preview -->
                <div id="image-preview" style="display: none; margin-top: 10px;">
                    <img src="" alt="Preview" style="max-width: 100%; max-height: 200px; border-radius: 8px;">
                    <button type="button" id="remove-image-btn" class="btn-small" style="margin-top: 5px;">Remove</button>
                </div>
                
                <div class="modal-actions">
                    <button id="submit-post">Post</button>
                    <button id="cancel-post">Cancel</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div id="js-lightbox" class="js-lightbox hidden">
            <span class="js-lightbox-close">&times;</span>
            <img src="" alt="Expanded view">
        </div>

        <script src="/script.js"></script>
    </body>
</html>